    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Hypostomus krikati sp. n. Holotype, CICCAA 01731, 209.3 mm SL; Brazil, State of Maranhão, Municipality of Bom Jesus das Selvas, Pindaré River drainage, Mearim River basin, northeastern Brazil." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7426698/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7426700>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Intraspecific variation in snout tip of Hypostomus krikati sp. n. A. 01731, 209.3 mm SL, plated tip. B. CICCAA 06159, 204.1 mm SL, naked tip. C. CIUEMA 1300, 191.9 mm SL, partially naked tip." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7426700/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7426702>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Predorsal squamation pattern.A. Hypostomus krikati sp. n. (CICCAA 07109) 99.1 mm SL. B. Hypostomus pusarum (CICCAA 07108) 81. 5 mm SL. Red = predosal plate. Green = acessory predorsal plates. Yellow = supraoccipital plate. Blue = pterotic-supracleithrum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7426702/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7426706>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Hypostomus krikati sp. n. (CIUEMA 1300) 191.9 mm SL. A. Keels of lateral plate series. B. Tip of pectoral fin." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7426706/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7426704>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Distribution of Hypostomus krikati sp. n. Paratypes (red circles) and holotype (black circle). Mearim River basin in orange." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7426704/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

